## 2. Gate Approval Checklist

```
GATE APPROVAL REQUIREMENTS & SIGN-OFF

GATE 1: STRATEGIC FIT APPROVAL
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Approval Authority: Chief Digital Officer + Executive Steering Committee
Timeline: Week 2 (after ideation phase)
Duration of Review: 2 weeks

Pre-Gate Checklist:
☐ Initiative proposal document completed
☐ Business case developed (preliminary)
☐ Strategic alignment assessed (score documented)
☐ Stakeholder consultation completed (>75% support)
☐ Budget availability confirmed with Finance
☐ High-level risk assessment documented
☐ Executive sponsors identified & committed
☐ Governance board briefed

Gate Review Meeting:
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Attendance: CDO, Sponsor, Finance Lead, Key Stakeholders   │
│ Duration: 2 hours                                          │
│ Decision Framework:                                         │
│                                                             │
│ 1. Strategic Alignment Score: 0-10 (Target: 8+)           │
│    Questions: Does this align with digital strategy?      │
│               Will it support policy objectives?          │
│                                                             │
│ 2. Political Support: Yes/No (Must have Minister level)   │
│    Questions: Is there executive commitment?             │
│               Will this survive political changes?        │
│                                                             │
│ 3. Budget Feasibility: Approved / Need clarification      │
│    Questions: Is funding available & allocated?           │
│               Are costs realistic?                        │
│                                                             │
│ 4. Stakeholder Support: % (Target: >75%)                  │
│    Questions: Are key stakeholders aligned?              │
│               Are concerns documented & plans to address? │
│                                                             │
│ 5. Risk Assessment: Acceptable / Needs mitigation         │
│    Questions: Are major risks identified?                │
│               Are risk owners assigned?                   │
│                                                             │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Approval Decision:
☐ APPROVED → Proceed to Stage 2 (Requirements & Design)
☐ APPROVED WITH CONDITIONS → List conditions; set review date
☐ DEFERRED → Schedule follow-up review (3 months)
☐ REJECTED → Document reasons; offer re-submission guidelines

